dct_title_s: Plan de ville. 1:12 500, 1 cm = 125 m, plan des transports, numéros de rues, sens uniques, index des rues, parkings
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Insets: Recto: Le Croisic [continued on verso] -- Verso : Guérande. Includes index, local transit map, coverage and location maps. Companion index includes map on cover of "Centre ville de Saint-Nazaire." Location map on verso of cover.
